Installing Propel (Pervasive fork)
==================================

This fork is installed with Composer:

    composer require tbl0605/propel1-pervasive

Development setup:

    git clone https://github.com/tbl0605/Propel-pervasive.git
    cd Propel-pervasive
    composer install

See README.md for running tests.

Legacy PEAR packages are published as release artifacts on GitHub, not via pear.propelorm.org.

For general Propel 1.x usage, see: http://www.propelorm.org/documentation/
